hopobject.body: I went to womens best shaker bottle However painful currently, this could all prove an important lesson for Hodgson heading into a World Cup year when player anguish about omission will be most raw and the media spotlight most acute. He will understand that every word and action, even in the presumed privacy of the dressing-room, will be analysed. The path to the World Cup, sadly, will not run smoothly. It’s not just the scourge of injuries that can distract and disrupt. There is usually the pre-tournament story.
